{"tid":391292,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有工可以介紹比我屋企人？","createTime":"2017-09-07T16:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T16:32:56.000Z","uid":18227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3229725d11772c8a04611ae3580ca3b4f426b080","tid":391292,"uid":18227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:05:22.000Z","msg":"由於我媽日日無所事事，賭博成癮 最近連左去左8日澳門先肯返屋企。所以都傾過 希望可以搵份工固定佢生活，唔可以再咁賭落去。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有工可以介紹啊，但唔好大辛苦，此終年紀開似大又女人。而佢咩學歷都冇，搵到份萬零蚊就可以啦"},{"pid":"5b8ccaccec62aabb4ffc57789c48fd7feb18a4da","tid":391292,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"保安"},{"pid":"2eade255692ca117f8cadda1b8dc24bfc63d2657","tid":391292,"uid":18227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保安</blockquote><br />\n佢曾經帶奶粉過關 比人捉左 有案底 拎唔到保安牌"},{"pid":"8687c2493db75d84b2988d9a20b8fcb2481ee2bf","tid":391292,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"無學歷想唔辛苦又有萬令蚊.... 應該無乜..."},{"pid":"9e62472627c71182cabc570172b35cf2379450f6","tid":391292,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"譚仔呀姐"},{"pid":"9605f5e06c5020926110e65773f81e5fdf7b75f9","tid":391292,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"月台助理，幾千蚊"},{"pid":"7a295e22857bc523baeed7f5ddfe3712702cfc46","tid":391292,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"唔辛苦 唔洗學歷 每月有萬零蚊  應該大把人去搶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如去政府進修 學整點心 剪髮 陪月 不過搵唔到咩錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ca94fd8c9c2cfec5af4d3fbe44a603acfd630d","tid":391292,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"唔想辛苦 冇學歷 有案底的話<br />\n不如唔好撚萬幾蚊既工<br />\n做下家務助理咁算啦 都係